snippet.title: Dreamcast Longplay: Red Dog Superior Firepower
snippet.description:
If you were following my old walkthrough and don't feel like rewatching the first few missions all over again, fear not, you can select each mission down below.

Well over a year ago, I started working on an walkthrough for Dreamcast's Red Dog, but unfortunately, at the time, I lost my motivation to work on it, and the walkthough was put on holds.

Recently, I decided that I had to finish it, and that I would do so whenever I got the chance, therefore I restarted the thing all over again in the form of this Longplay, hope you enjoy it.
